One system. One simplified process. Confirmation.com
Confirmation.com is your all-in-one online audit confirmation solution. Offering a central repository to house all confirmation data and a multitude of powerful, intelligent features puts you in control of the entire process and ensures that client data is secure throughout transmission. Everything you need to effectively manage the audit confirmation process is contained within a single, convenient, feature-packed platform.
 
Consider the value:

Puts you in control of the process—with the ability to manage the audit confirmation process from within a single, cloud-based platform, you maintain control every step of the way. Additionally, sophisticated validation features helps you avoid having to perform your own validation procedures.
Improves confirmation fraud detection—the system enhances your ability to detect confirmation fraud.
Handles a variety of confirmation requests—including accounts receivable, accounts payable, bank, EBP, and legal; all within one system.
Supports both electronic and paper confirmation requests—allowing maximum flexibility in how you to manage process.
Offers unprecedented data security—Confirmation.com operates in a highly secure and controlled environment to protect privacy and confidentiality of user data.
Presents you with an intuitive interface—allowing you to easily navigate through the system to monitor status updates, download reports, and review dynamic statistics and company-wide updates and features.
Offers a long list of intelligently designed features that further accelerate process efficiency.





