Capital Confirmation, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 7:31 PM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of Capital Confirmation, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Capital Confirmation, Inc. provides an online audit confirmation platform for auditors and accounting firms to manage various aspects of the audit confirmation process. It offers in-network and out-of-network AR/AP confirmations, in-network and out-of-network bank confirmations, employee benefit plan confirmations, and legal confirmations. The company handles various confirmation requests in electronic and paper formats. It serves banks, companies, and law firms in the United States and internationally. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Brentwood, Tennessee with an additional office in Japan.


214 Centerview DriveSuite 265Brentwood, TN 37027United StatesFounded in 2000



