Capital Confirmation, Inc. Key Developments

Confirmation.com Announces Expansion with Presence in Canada and Mexico; Appoints Executives
Mar 29 17
Confirmation.com announced the expansion of its services in both Mexico and Canada. The strategic location of these two new offices will add value and industry benchmarks for both Confirmation.com and their clients. 

Alfredo Borgaro, joins Confirmation.com to lead the company's growth initiative in Mexico, and Amy Folkard will lead efforts in Canada.


Confirmation.com Expands to Japan; Appoints Matthew Grace to Lead the Growth Initiative for Japan
Jul 19 16
Confirmation.com announced the opening of an office in Japan as part of its continued expansion in Asia. Matthew Grace, with more than 20 years of experience in the international financial services market, joins Confirmation.com to lead the company's growth initiative for Japan. This new office satisfies the growing demand from Japanese auditors wanting to use Confirmation.com to better manage their audit confirmation requests. With Confirmation.com, any business, financial institution, or law firm that responds to audit confirmation requests will experience a more efficient, paperless process and be able to provide quicker responses.


Confirmation.com Announces Opening of New Office in Cyprus
Jul 13 16
Confirmation.com announced the opening of an office in Cyprus as part of its global expansion initiative. Located in Nicosia, this new office offers the company an opportunity to expand its market position in Cyprus, and other European and Middle Eastern markets.


