Invoicing Procedures and Payments
At the time you request a credit inquiry but before the credit inquiries are sent
        to the financial institutions, you will be provided an online invoice for you to
        approve. If you approve the online invoice you will be emailed a copy of the invoice
        for your records and simultaneously will be charged the invoice amount using your
        credit card on file with www.CreditConfirm.com through our credit card processor
